asset.title: 2009 - 2014 Nissan Maxima 3.5L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2009-2013 Nissan Maxima 3.5L.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-7002TTK

K&N 69-7002TTK air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 13.2 horsepower at 5249 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer.

K&N 69-7002TTK fits the following: 
2014 NISSAN MAXIMA 3.5L V6 
2013 NISSAN MAXIMA 3.5L V6 
2012 NISSAN MAXIMA 3.5L V6 
2011 NISSAN MAXIMA 3.5L V6 
2010 NISSAN MAXIMA 3.5L V6 
2009 NISSAN MAXIMA 3.5L V6 

Visit the product page to see an up to date list of vehicle models this air intake fits.
